      "span_text": "Alternatively, the Inputoutput BHTMM (IO-BHTMM)  defines a nonhomogenous approach that allows learning the input-conditional model P(y n |x n , θ), where the input tree x n conditions the generative process of an output structure y n that, in a supervised-learning interpretation, might be understood as the target."
